			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_head010",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "实现路径",
			"x": -1480,
			"y": 100,
			"width": 860,
			"height": 90,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_skill011",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "test-driven-development\n先写失败测试，再写最小实现通过。\n触发：做新功能、修 bug、重构时。",
			"x": -1480,
			"y": 220,
			"width": 860,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_skill012",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "justfile\n创建或管理 Justfile，把命令流程沉淀成任务。\n触发：有一组常用命令要标准化、简化时。",
			"x": -1480,
			"y": 420,
			"width": 860,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_head013",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "调试路径",
			"x": -580,
			"y": 100,
			"width": 860,
			"height": 90,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_skill014",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "systematic-debugging\n按步骤定位 bug，避免拍脑袋改。\n触发：遇到 test failure、异常行为或未知 bug 时。",
			"x": -580,
			"y": 220,
			"width": 860,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_skill015",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "investigate\n系统查根因，先搞明白为什么坏掉。\n触发：用户报 bug、异常或行为不对时。",
			"x": -580,
			"y": 420,
			"width": 860,
			"height": 170,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_ftitle016",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "本域主线\ntest-driven-development → justfile → systematic-debugging → investigate",
			"x": 500,
			"y": 100,
			"width": 1300,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_flow017",
