		{
			"id": "t_decision024",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "何时选 A / B\n- 做功能：test-driven-development\n- 命令常用且重复：justfile\n- 问题原因不明：systematic-debugging / investigate",
			"x": 500,
			"y": 1180,
			"width": 1300,
			"height": 220,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_adj025",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "相邻域推荐\n- 研究与文档\n- QA评审与验证",
			"x": -1480,
			"y": 1640,
			"width": 820,
			"height": 240,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "t_warn026",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "常见误用提醒\n- 不要跳过红绿循环。\n- investigate / systematic-debugging 先定位，再改代码。",
